Direct Known Subclasses:
ArtifactLinkPublisherTask, LogLinkPublisherTask
public class LinkPublisherTask
extends AbstractPublisherTask

Ant task to add a link-type contribution to a build result.

Required attributes are:

  • label - The label for the build result contribution.
  • url - The url that the link contribution points to.
Optional attributes are:
  • status - The status of the contribution. One of OK, INFO, WARNING, ERROR. The default is OK.
See AbstractPublisherTask for additional required and optional attributes.

Since:
0.5
